OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772676194
OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FThe government has announced the first
OL,7,Frepatriation flight for British
OL,8,Fcitizens in the Middle East, saying it
OL,9,Fwill leave on Wednesday evening. It
OL,10,Fcomes as the Prime Minister faced
OL,11,Fcriticism from US President Donald
OL,12,FTrump over the conflict in the Middle
OL,13,FEast.
OL,15,FIsrael targeted the Iranian leadership
OL,16,Fand security forces with dawn strikes
OL,17,Fon Tehran and other major cities.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
