FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772676194
OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FThe Islamic Republic responded with
OL,7,Fmissile barrages and swarms of drone
OL,8,Fattacks on Israel and across the
OL,9,FPersian Gulf region.
OL,11,FBlasts could be heard on Wednesday
OL,12,Fmorning as the IDF carried out a
OL,13,Fseries of strikes "on the Basij and
OL,14,Finternal security command centres in
OL,15,FTehran belonging to the Iranian terror
OL,16,Fregime", it said on a post on X.
OL,18,F"The targeted command centers were
OL,19,Fused by the Iranian regime to maintain
OL,20,Fcontrol throughout Iran," the
OL,21,Fstatement added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772676194
OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FIsrael said its air defences had been
OL,7,Factivated to intercept Iranian
OL,8,Fmissiles targeting Israel, with
OL,9,Fexplosions heard around Jerusalem.
OL,11,FOn Tuesday, the building where Iranian
OL,12,Fclerics will meet to select a new
OL,13,Fsupreme leader in the holy city of Qom
OL,14,Fwas reportedly hit.
OL,16,FWith Iran's stranglehold on tanker
OL,17,Fmovement through the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,18,FBrent crude prices rose to more than
OL,19,F$82 a barrel, up more than 13% since
OL,20,Fthe start of the conflict and at its
OL,21,Fhighest price since July 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772676194
OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FIn response to attacks, Iran's
OL,7,Fparamilitary Revolutionary Guard
OL,8,Flaunched 40 ballistic missiles at
OL,9,Ftargets associated with the US
OL,10,Fmilitary in the Middle East, according
OL,11,Fto state media.
OL,13,FIt said it targeted Irbil in Iraq, two
OL,14,Fmilitary bases in Kuwait, and two US
OL,15,Fwarships.
OL,17,FThe US and Israel launched joint
OL,18,Fstrikes on Saturday morning, killing
OL,19,Fthe Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali
OL,20,FKhamenei.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772676194
OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FThe conflict soon spread across the
OL,7,FMiddle East, with Iran striking
OL,8,Ftargets in the Gulf states.
OL,10,FUS Navy Adm. Brad Cooper, the head of
OL,11,FU.S. Central Command, described the
OL,12,FAmerican strikes in the opening hours
OL,13,Fof the campaign as "nearly double the
OL,14,Fscale" of the initial attacks during
OL,15,Fthe 2003 US-led invasion of Iraq.
OL,17,FThe conflict continues across the
OL,18,FMiddle East, with the American embassy
OL,19,Fin Saudi Arabia and the US Consulate
OL,20,Fin the United Arab Emirates coming
OL,21,Funder drone attacks on Tuesday.
OL,26,@uD@TOUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
