OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FThe US has urged non-emergency
OL,7,Fgovernment personnel to evacuate the
OL,8,Fkingdom.
OL,10,FThe UK government has announced it has
OL,11,Fchartered a repatriation flight from
OL,12,FOman on Wednesday for UK nationals
OL,13,Fseeking to leave the Middle East due
OL,14,Fto the ongoing conflict in the region.
OL,16,FThe foreign office said the flight
OL,17,Fwill depart Muscat at 7 pm and is
OL,18,Favailable for British nationals, their
OL,19,Fpartners and children under 18 with a
OL,20,Fvalid travel document.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772676194
OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FAccording to the Foreign Office,
OL,7,Fpriority for the evacuation flight
OL,8,Fwill be given to the most vulnerable,
OL,9,Fand they will contact British
OL,10,Fnationals in Oman.
OL,12,FAnyone who registered their presence
OL,13,Fin the United Arab Emirates (UAE) and
OL,14,Fare now in Oman is asked to register
OL,15,Ffor a place on a flight.
OL,17,FBeirut woke up to the sound of drones
OL,18,Foverhead on Wednesday, as several
OL,19,Ftowns and a hotel in a suburb were hit
OL,20,Fby strikes overnight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
