OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FAt least six people were killed in
OL,7,FIsraeli strikes on towns near Beirut,
OL,8,Faccording to Lebanon's Health Ministry.
OL,10,FThe towns of Aramoun and Saadiyat,
OL,11,Fjust south of Beirut's international
OL,12,Fairport, were struck, with a further
OL,13,Feight people wounded.
OL,15,FA hotel in the Beirut suburb of
OL,16,FHazmieh was also hit, but there have
OL,17,Fbeen no immediate reports of
OL,18,Fcasualties.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
