PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772676194
OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FThe strikes came without warning, with
OL,7,Fthe Israeli military not immediately
OL,8,Fdisclosing the targets.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, the death toll has risen
OL,11,Ffrom a strike that hit a residential
OL,12,Fcomplex in Baalbeck, according to the
OL,13,Fstate-run National News Agency
OL,15,F15 others were wounded, and three
OL,16,Fremain missing, it reported.
