OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FUnited Arab Emirates (UAE) & Saudi
OL,7,FArabia
OL,9,FThe US State Department said Wednesday
OL,10,Fit had authorised non-emergency
OL,11,Fgovernment personnel to evacuate the
OL,12,Fkingdom after the American Embassy in
OL,13,FSaudi Arabia and the US Consulate in
OL,14,Fthe United Arab Emirates came under
OL,15,Fdrone attacks on Tuesday.
OL,17,FFour US Service Members killed during
OL,18,Fthe conflict with Iran identified
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
