OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772676194
OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FMeanwhile, four US service members
OL,7,Fkilled in a deadly Iranian drone
OL,8,Fstrike in Kuwait have been named.
OL,10,FThey were named as: Captain Cody A.
OL,11,FKhork, 35, of Winter Haven, Florida;
OL,12,FSergeant Noah L Tietjens, 42, of
OL,13,FBellevue, Nebraska; Sergeant Nicole M.
OL,14,FAmor, 39, of White Bear Lake,
OL,15,FMinnesota, and Specialist Declan J.
OL,16,FCoady, 20, of West Des Moines, Iowa.
OL,18,FThe Pentagon said they were all killed
OL,19,Fby a drone that struck where they were
OL,20,Fworking in Port Shuabia, Kuwait, on
OL,21,FSunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772676194
OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FTwo other soldiers who were killed in
OL,7,Fthe strike have not been publicly
OL,8,Fidentified.
OL,10,FMeanwhile, on Tuesday, US President
OL,11,FDonald Trump repeated earlier
OL,12,Fcriticisms of the UK government's
OL,13,Fstance towards the conflict in Iran,
OL,14,Fsaying Starmer is "not Winston
OL,15,FChurchill".
OL,17,FSpeaking alongside German Chancellor
OL,18,FFriedrich Merz, Trump said he is "not
OL,19,Fhappy" with the UK and with Starmer,
OL,20,Fand that "this is not Winston
OL,21,FChurchill that we're dealing with".
OL,26,@zD@bOU{D@FO]|D@JOU}D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
