OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772676194
OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FThe president also floated the idea of
OL,7,Fescorting oil tankers through the
OL,8,FStrait of Hormuz with the US Navy
OL,9,Fafter Iran threatened to close the
OL,10,Fcritical shipping lane.
OL,12,FHe said the US Navy could escort
OL,13,Ftankers through the Strait of Hormuz
OL,14,F"if necessary", after shipping traffic
OL,15,Falmost entirely halted through the key
OL,16,Ftrade passage following threats from
OL,17,FIran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
