OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FHis comments came as the UK announced
OL,7,Fit would send helicopters and an air
OL,8,Fdefence destroyer to Cyprus in
OL,9,Fresponse to the growing conflict in
OL,10,Fthe Middle East.
OL,12,FThe prime minister confirmed the UK
OL,13,Fwould be sending the HMS Dragon, one
OL,14,Fof the Royal Navy's six Type 45 air
OL,15,Fdefence destroyers, after RAF Akrotiri
OL,16,Fon Cyprus was hit by a drone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
