OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772676194
OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FThe announcement comes after France
OL,7,Fsaid it would send its only aircraft
OL,8,Fcarrier and a contingent of warships
OL,9,Fto bolster its anti-drone defences in
OL,10,Fthe region.
OL,12,FBritish nationals abroad
OL,14,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said
OL,15,Fon Monday that 130,000 British
OL,16,Fnationals have registered their
OL,17,Fpresence in the region. She previously
OL,18,Fsaid a total of around 300,000 British
OL,19,Fcitizens are in Gulf countries
OL,20,Ftargeted by Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
