OL,3,CIsrael targets Iran's leadership as
OL,4,CTehran continues strikes on Gulf
OL,6,FA government charter flight will also
OL,7,Ftake off from Muscat, Oman, "in the
OL,8,Fcoming days".
OL,10,FBritish nationals are being advised to
OL,11,Ffollow the instructions of local
OL,12,Fauthorities and monitor the Foreign
OL,13,FOffice's travel advice, which
OL,14,Fofficials expect to change rapidly.
OL,16,FPreviously safe havens in the Middle
OL,17,FEast, such as Dubai, have seen
OL,18,Fincoming fire and hundreds of
OL,19,Fthousands of airline passengers are
OL,20,Fstranded around the globe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
